com.facebook.buck.android.toolchain

Class AbstractAndroidPlatformTarget

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.android.toolchain.AbstractAndroidPlatformTarget
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Toolchain
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AndroidPlatformTarget

    @Value.Immutable(builder=false,
                 copy=false)
public abstract class AbstractAndroidPlatformTarget
extends Object
implements Toolchain
    Represents a platform to target for Android. Eventually, it should be possible to construct an arbitrary platform target, but currently, we only recognize a fixed set of targets.
